n van laaggeletterdheid herkennen en bespreekbaar te maken. Is dit niet direct gelukt? Geen zorgen; na ieder gesprek ontvang je feedback en tips die je kunt toepassen in de volgende ronde.\n\nDeze unieke gespreksimulatie maakt gebruik van vrije spraak, waardoor het initiatief in het gesprek bij jou ligt. Door de realistische omgeving en je virtuele gesprekspartner, word je helemaal ondergedompeld in de situatie. Met de ingebouwde feedback en intelligente begeleiding krijg je jouw gespreksvaardigheden op een hoger niveau.", "short_description": "Oefen met het herkennen en bespreekbaar maken van laaggeletterdheid in Virtual Reality."}]}, "developer_name": null, "developer_privacy_policy_url": "https://cdn.jutten.com/docs/Privacyverklaring_The_Simulation_Crew_1.1.pdf", "developer_terms_of_service_url": null, "publisher_name": "The Simulation Crew BV", "support_website_url": "https://thesimulationcrew.nl/contact/", "website_url": "https://thesimulationcrew.nl/", "category": null, "comfort_rating": "NOT_RATED", "comfort_tags": [], "context_category": {"id": "362692211442873", "context_category": "APPS"}, "context_topics": [{"id": "27362927396627898"}], "external_subscription_type": "REQUIRED", "genres": [], "has_in_app_ads": null, "internet_connection": "REQUIRED", "play_area": "NO_MOVEMENT", "recommended_graphics": null, "recommended_memory_gb": null, "recommended_processor": null, "supported_in_app_languages": ["nl"], "supported_input_devices": ["OCULUS_TOUCH"], "supported_player_modes": ["SITTING", "STANDING", "ROOM_SCALE"], "supported_tracking_modes": [], "user_interaction_modes": ["SINGLE_USER"], "id": "7107855689335535"}}]}, "scheduled_offers": {"count": 1, "nodes": [{"status": "PUBLISHED", "id": "928778155543144"}]}, "baseline_offer": {"id": "928778155543144"}, "is_approved": true, "firstOffer": {"nodes": [{"start_time": 1714600200, "status": "PUBLISHED", "id": "928778155543144"}]}, "liveChannel": {"nodes": [{"latest_supported_binary": {"__typename": "AndroidBinar